 {"id":"asupersync-3qv04.4.1","title":"[WASM][Packages] Create real package tree and manifests","description":"Create the actual package directory structure and manifests for the declared Browser Edition package set: @asupersync/browser-core, @asupersync/browser, @asupersync/react, and @asupersync/next. The goal is to make the documented package topology exist physically in the repo, with ownership and layering enforced by code rather than prose alone.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"VioletDeer","estimated_minutes":240,"created_at":"2026-03-06T07:17:33.291538607Z","created_by":"CopperForest","updated_at":"2026-03-07T03:59:05.190279371Z","closed_at":"2026-03-07T03:59:05.190254995Z","close_reason":"Materialized Browser Edition package tree with committed package manifests and Rust contract checks for manifest discovery and internal layering","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["npm","packages","typescript","wasm"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"asupersync-3qv04.4.1","depends_on_id":"asupersync-3qv04.2.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-06T07:19:04.871351983Z","created_by":"CopperForest","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"asupersync-3qv04.4.1","depends_on_id":"asupersync-3qv04.4","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-06T07:17:33.291538607Z","created_by":"CopperForest","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}],"comments":[{"id":2405,"issue_id":"asupersync-3qv04.4.1","author":"CopperForest","text":"Package reality check captured for future readers:

The desired package topology is documented, but the repo does not yet contain the physical package artifacts that users would consume. During recon there was no `packages/` tree, no `pkg/` directory, and no `package.json` manifests corresponding to the documented Browser Edition package set.

